Handblock vs Machine Printing, what’s the difference?👀

While machine printing is faster and often machine-led, handblock printing is an age-old craft done entirely by hand, with each block carefully stamped to create beautiful patterns.✨

Our Solitaire Collection is 100% handblock printed made by skilled artisans using wooden blocks, with no shortcuts. That’s why it’s not just clothing, it’s art we deeply value💙💚

(The Indian Ethnic Co, New Drop, Handcrafted, Clothing, Cotton, Solitaire, Indigo, Artisans)
